Translation data will be focused on `.\lot\x\language\state\id.php` file. If you want to contribute, be sure to follow
the data in that file.

Open the `.\state.php` file to add `language` property with a value of the supported language code as listed in the
`.\lot\x\language\state` folder:

~~~ .php
<?php

return [
    // …
    'language' => 'id' // Change site language to “Indonesian”
];
~~~

